snippet.title: Woh Chaand Kahan Se Laogi (Official Video) Vishal Mishra | Urvashi Rautela, Mohsin Khan |Muntashir M
snippet.description:
VYRL Originals brings to you Vishal Mishra’s next masterpiece Woh Chaand Kahan Se Laogi an expression of every lover who has loved and been betrayed in a relationship. The music video features the gorgeous Urvashi Rautela and TV’s heartthrob Mohsin Khan. The duo portrays the story of love, heartbreak and resilience captured by director Arif Khan and lyrics beautifully penned by Manoj Muntashir.

Watch till the end, as the video will leave you with a feeling that some betrayals help you foster the pain to forge your success in the future and can heal in ways one can never imagine.

#VishalMishra #UrvashiRautela #MohsinKhan

snippet.localized.description:

snippet.description:

Episode 2940:
----------------------
Popatlal tries to make fried snacks for the breakfast but he notices that he does not have any tomato sauce in the house to have with the snacks. So, he tries to call Abdul, but Abdul does not pick his phone up. Popatlal then comes out in the balcony of his house and shouts Abdul’s name. Bhide and others notice Popatlal shouting so they ask him the reason for his yelling. Popatlal tells everyone that he has made some fried snacks and he needs some tomato sauce to eat with it. Bhide tells Popatlal that he will give him the tomato sauce. Later, Bhide goes to Popatlal with a bottle of tomato sauce and leaves. When Popatlal notices that the tomato is expired he comes downstairs screaming Bhide’s name. What will Popatlal do now? Let’s find out.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. snippet.title: தீபத்திற்கு முதல் நாள் ஏற்ற வேண்டிய பரணி தீபம் ஏற்றும் முறை, எண்ணிக்கை & பலன்கள் | Bharani Deepam
snippet.description:
#கார்த்திகைதீபம் #பரணிதீபம் #Bharanideepam

கார்த்திகை தீபம் 2020 தீபம் ஏற்றும் நேரம், எண்ணிக்கை, இடம், வழிபடும் முறை & பலன்கள்|Karthigai Deepam
https://youtu.be/QzUvI5DqYnE

பொதுவாக கார்த்திகை தீபம் அனைவரும் அறிந்ததே.  ஆனால் கார்த்திகை தீபத்திற்கு முந்தைய நாளில் பலரும் தீபம் ஏற்றினாலும் அது எதற்காக ஏற்றப்படுகிறது? எத்தனை தீபங்கள் ஏற்ற வேண்டும்? ஏற்றுவதால் கிடைக்கும் பலன்கள் என்பது பலருக்கும் தெரிவதில்லை.  இந்தப் பதிவில் திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் பரணி தீபத்தைப் பற்றிய விளக்கம் அளித்துள்ளார். 


- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம் 

# திருக்கார்த்திகை 
# கார்த்திகை தீபம் 
# பரணி தீபம் 
# Karthigai Deepam
# Bharani Deepam

snippet.title: നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ മകള്‍ അയിഷയുടെ വിവാഹനിശ്ചയത്തില്‍ കുടുംബസമേതം ദിലീപ് l Nadhirsha Doughter Engagement
snippet.description:
സിനിമാലോകത്ത് നാളുകളായി വിവാഹവും വിവാഹനിശ്ചയ വാര്‍ത്തകളുമാണ് നിറയുന്നത്. നിരവധി താരപുത്രന്മാരും പുത്രികളുമായി വിവാഹിത രായത്. ഇപ്പോള്‍ നടനും സംവിധായകനുെനാക്കെയായ നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ മകളുടെ വിവാഹനിശ്ചയ ചിത്രങ്ങളാണ് സോഷ്യല്‍ മീഡിയ കീഴടക്കുന്നത്.  കോവിഡ് മാനദണ്ഡങ്ങള്‍ പാലിച്ചാണ് ചടങ്ങ് നടന്നത്. നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ ഉറ്റ സുഹൃത്ത് ദിലീപ് കുടുംബ സമേതമാണ് ചടങ്ങിനെത്തിയത്. കാസര്‍കോട്ടെ പ്രമുഖ വ്യവസായിയായ ലത്തീഫ് ഉപ്പള ഗേറ്റിന്റെ മകനാണ് വരന്‍. സിനിമാരംഗത്തെ ഉറ്റ സുഹൃത്തുക്കളും ബന്ധുക്കളുമാണ് ചടങ്ങില്‍ പങ്കെടുത്തത്. നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ മകള്‍ ആയിഷ മലയാളി താരം നമിത പ്രമോദിന്റെ ഉറ്റ കൂട്ടുകാരിയാണ്.

സിനിമാലോകത്ത് നാളുകളായി വിവാഹവും വിവാഹനിശ്ചയ വാര്‍ത്തകളുമാണ് നിറയുന്നത്. നിരവധി താരപുത്രന്മാരും പുത്രികളുമായി വിവാഹിത രായത്. ഇപ്പോള്‍ നടനും സംവിധായകനുെനാക്കെയായ നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ മകളുടെ വിവാഹനിശ്ചയ ചിത്രങ്ങളാണ് സോഷ്യല്‍ മീഡിയ കീഴടക്കുന്നത്.  കോവിഡ് മാനദണ്ഡങ്ങള്‍ പാലിച്ചാണ് ചടങ്ങ് നടന്നത്. നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ ഉറ്റ സുഹൃത്ത് ദിലീപ് കുടുംബ സമേതമാണ് ചടങ്ങിനെത്തിയത്. കാസര്‍കോട്ടെ പ്രമുഖ വ്യവസായിയായ ലത്തീഫ് ഉപ്പള ഗേറ്റിന്റെ മകനാണ് വരന്‍. സിനിമാരംഗത്തെ ഉറ്റ സുഹൃത്തുക്കളും ബന്ധുക്കളുമാണ് ചടങ്ങില്‍ പങ്കെടുത്തത്. നാദിര്‍ഷയുടെ മകള്‍ ആയിഷ മലയാളി താരം നമിത പ്രമോദിന്റെ ഉറ്റ കൂട്ടുകാരിയാണ്.

#Nadirshah  #AyishaShah  #Engagement #Dileep #kavyaMadhavan #Meenakshi #NamithaPramod # KhadeejaShah #ShahinaShah

snippet.title: We are taking a break ! Leaving Saudi Arabia ! Cargo Packing !
snippet.description:
This video might be a surprise for most of you. Yes, we are leaving Saudi Arabia and moving back to our homeland, Kerala. Lots of plans and there’s more surprises coming up. Will let you know soon. Till then stay tuned and do watch this video of few moments taken here and there. Few shopping, few me-time moments, few family time and so on. 

Saudi Arabia is a country where I found myself. I got an identity from here and will always be thankful for the warmth and shelter this country had provided us. Initially it was tough, but  gradually became in love with this beautiful land.

We badly needed a break from all the stress revolving around. Really happy and positive with the decision, to spend sometime with our family back in Kerala. 

We had to shift many stuff, specially crockeries. We approached a team with very reasonable rate. If you are in Saudi Arabia and looking forward for sea cargo, Please contact the below person.

Mr. Mohammed Saleeth
Mob : +966582971155
Landline :+966114120007

snippet.title: तुलसी विवाह की कथा || Tulsi Vivah Ki Katha || तुलसी विवाह की कहानी || Tulsi Vivah ki kahani
snippet.description:
तुलसी विवाह की कथा | Tulsi Vivah Ki Katha  || Tulsi Vivah ki kahani
कार्तिक महीने के देव-उठावनी एकादशी का दिन तुलसी विवाह के रूप में मनाया जाता है। जो मनुष्य  शालिग्राम  के साथ तुलसी का विवाह करेगा उसे इस लोक और परलोक में विपुल यश प्राप्त होगा। तुलसी विवाह के संबंध में कई कथाएं प्रचलित हैं। तुलसी विवाह की कथा का यह वीडियो तुलसी शालिग्राम विवाह की दो कहानियाँ प्रस्तुत करता है। पहली तुलसी विवाह की कहानी ननद-भाभी की है।  दूसरी तुलसी विवाह की कहानी रानी वृंदा की तुलसी में रूपांतरित होने की प्रसिद्ध कहानी है। आइए हम तुलसी शालिग्राम विवाह कथा देखते हैं और तुलसी से प्रार्थना करते हैं कि वे हमें आशीर्वाद दें जैसे कि उन्होंने तुलसी विवाह में अपने भक्त को आशीर्वाद दिया

Tulsi Vivah will be performed on 25 November, 2020. Tulsi Vivah can be performed once a year only on Dev Uthani ekadashi day. Tulsi Vivah is performed on Kartik maas Shukla Ekadashi. This video of Tulsi vivah ki katha presents two stories of Tulsi Shaligram vivah. The first Tulsi vivah ki kahani is about a lady and her sister in law. The second Tulsi vivah ki kahani is famous story of Queen Vrinda transforming into Tulsi. Let us watch Tulsi Shaligram marriage story and pray to Tulsi to bless us like she blessed her devotee in Tulsi Vivah ki kahani

#tulsivivah #tulsivivah2020 #तुलसीविवाह

snippet.title: Major Beginnings | 'The Look' Test | Adivi Sesh | Sashi Kiran Tikka | Major The Film
snippet.description:
‘The film speaks about the way he lived, not about the way he lost life.’ 
November 27 is not just a remembrance day, but the day to celebrate Major #SandeepUnnikrishnan's life. We share this video in honour of the man who has instilled pride in a billion hearts.
#MajorTheFilm #MajorBeginnings

Based on the life of real-life Hero Major Sandeep Unnikrishnan, Major, the film, aims to show how this valiant soldier saved the lives of numerous hostages before being martyred by the activists who wreaked havoc in the Taj Mahal Palace Mumbai, India on the 26th of November, 2008.

Major, a bilingual Hindi and Telugu film has been produced by Sony Pictures Films India in association with Mahesh Babu's GMB Entertainment Pvt. Ltd. and A+S Movies. It is directed by acclaimed Telugu director Sashi Kiran Tikka and features Adivi Sesh, Sobhita Dhulipala and Saiee Manjrekar.

snippet.localized.description:
‘The film speaks about the way he lived, not about the way he lost life.’ 
November 27 is not just a remembrance day, but the day to celebrate Major #SandeepUnnikrishnan's life. We share this video in honour of the man who has instilled pride in a billion hearts.
#MajorTheFilm #MajorBeginnings

Based on the life of real-life Hero Major Sandeep Unnikrishnan, Major, the film, aims to show how this valiant soldier saved the lives of numerous hostages before being martyred by the activists who wreaked havoc in the Taj Mahal Palace Mumbai, India on the 26th of November, 2008.

Major, a bilingual Hindi and Telugu film has been produced by Sony Pictures Films India in association with Mahesh Babu's GMB Entertainment Pvt. Ltd. and A+S Movies. It is directed by acclaimed Telugu director Sashi Kiran Tikka and features Adivi Sesh, Sobhita Dhulipala and Saiee Manjrekar.

snippet.title: Lil Nas X Celebrates Thanksgiving With the Biggest Last Dab Ever | Hot Ones
snippet.description:
Happy Thanksgiving Spice Lords! Welcome to the 5th annual Thanksgiving Hot Ones with Lil Nas X! Lil Nas X is a 2x Grammy Award-winning artist you know from his breakout hit ‘Old Town Road,’ one of the biggest records in Billboard history. His latest single ‘Holiday’ is out now. snippet.title: Clifford The Big Red Dog - First Look - Paramount Pictures
snippet.description:
It’s here: your very first look at Clifford The Big Red Dog! #CliffordMovie hits theatres in 2021.
 
🐾
 
When middle-schooler Emily Elizabeth (Darby Camp) meets a magical animal rescuer (John Cleese) who gifts her a little, red puppy, she never anticipated waking up to find a giant ten-foot hound in her small New York City apartment. While her single mom (Sienna Guillory) is away for business, Emily and her fun but impulsive uncle Casey (Jack Whitehall) set out on an adventure that will keep you on the edge-of-your-seat as our heroes take a bite out of the Big Apple. Based on the beloved Scholastic book character, Clifford will teach the world how to love big!
  
🐾

snippet.title: [Performance] CHUNG HA 청하 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)' Performance Video
snippet.description:
CHUNG HA 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)' Performance Video

#CHUNGHA #청하 #R3HAB #DreamofYou #PerformanceVideo

Stream/ Download 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)' : https://ffm.to/chungha_dreamofyou
Subscribe CHUNG HA : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Gxb0gMCh3EPIDLQXeQUog

CHUNG HA, R3HAB Collaboration Single 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)'

K-Pop superstar CHUNG HA releases a collaboration single with world famous DJ & Producer R3HAB. “Dream of You (with R3HAB)” is an electronic/dance track that combines a house beat and a thick bassline. A masterpiece is created from the beautiful harmony of retro sounds generated by strings, brass, and vocoder mixed with the dreamlike sound from the synthesizer. The vocal chopping elements heard within the intro are arranged throughout the song to make the single even more charismatic. You can once again experience the charm of CHUNG HA’s deep mid to low vocals, as heard in her recent single ‘Bad Boy.” This single “Dream of You (with R3HAB)” will excite your ears once again

'청하' 세계적인 DJ & 프로듀서 ‘R3HAB'과 컬래버레이션 싱글을 발매한다.
[Dream of You (with R3HAB)]는 하우스 리듬과 선이 굵은 베이스 라인이 이끄는 일렉트로닉 장르의 곡이다.
스트링, 브라스, 보코더의 레트로한 사운드와 몽환적인 신디사이저 사운드가 어우러져 거칠지만 아름다운 하나의 작품이 완성되었다. 인트로의 매력적인 찹핑 보이스 사운드가 곡의 곳곳에 배치되어 매력적으로 곡을 장식한다. 최근 싱글 'Bad Boy'부터 이어지는 '청하'의 중, 저음의 매력을 다시 한번 느낄 수 있다. 이번 싱글 [Dream of You (with R3HAB)]로 다시 한번 여러분의 귀를 즐겁게 자극할 예정이다.

snippet.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fernández, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

snippet.title: Fans in Argentina and Naples mourn death of Diego Maradona
snippet.description:
Football fans have gathered in large numbers in Diego Maradona's home country of Argentina after the icon of the sport died aged 60. Supporters congregated across Maradona's home city of Buenos Aires to pay tribute to the World Cup-winning captain. The Argentinian was also mourned in Naples where he spent seven seasons playing for Napoli FC

snippet.title: Olive and Mabel - still taking a paws.
snippet.description:
Really just wanted to say thank you for all the nice comments on all the videos. And sorry for a lack of new ones (which will come). Too much time being taken up by the book and I feel distinctly uncomfortable doing the shameless business of trying to promote it. But then, a whole lot of work went in to it and the best I can do is say that lots of people who have enjoyed the videos have also enjoyed the book. 'Olive, Mabel & Me' coming out in the USA and Canada on 1st December and already out elsewhere. 
Audiobook version coming soon.
Be careful out there...

CHUNG HA, R3HAB Collaboration Single 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)'

K-Pop superstar CHUNG HA releases a collaboration single with world famous DJ & Producer R3HAB. “Dream of You (with R3HAB)” is an electronic/dance track that combines a house beat and a thick bassline. A masterpiece is created from the beautiful harmony of retro sounds generated by strings, brass, and vocoder mixed with the dreamlike sound from the synthesizer. The vocal chopping elements heard within the intro are arranged throughout the song to make the single even more charismatic. You can once again experience the charm of CHUNG HA’s deep mid to low vocals, as heard in her recent single ‘Bad Boy.” This single “Dream of You (with R3HAB)” will excite your ears once again

'청하' 세계적인 DJ & 프로듀서 ‘R3HAB'과 컬래버레이션 싱글을 발매한다.
[Dream of You (with R3HAB)]는 하우스 리듬과 선이 굵은 베이스 라인이 이끄는 일렉트로닉 장르의 곡이다.
스트링, 브라스, 보코더의 레트로한 사운드와 몽환적인 신디사이저 사운드가 어우러져 거칠지만 아름다운 하나의 작품이 완성되었다. 인트로의 매력적인 찹핑 보이스 사운드가 곡의 곳곳에 배치되어 매력적으로 곡을 장식한다. 최근 싱글 'Bad Boy'부터 이어지는 '청하'의 중, 저음의 매력을 다시 한번 느낄 수 있다. 이번 싱글 [Dream of You (with R3HAB)]로 다시 한번 여러분의 귀를 즐겁게 자극할 예정이다.

snippet.title: Fans in Argentina and Naples mourn death of Diego Maradona
snippet.description:
Football fans have gathered in large numbers in Diego Maradona's home country of Argentina after the icon of the sport died aged 60. Supporters congregated across Maradona's home city of Buenos Aires to pay tribute to the World Cup-winning captain. The Argentinian was also mourned in Naples where he spent seven seasons playing for Napoli FC

snippet.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fernández, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

Lyrics:
You put me on a pedestal and tell me I’m the best
Raise me up into the sky until I’m short of breath
Fill me up with confidence, I say what’s in my chest
Spill my words and tear me down until there’s nothing left
Rearrange the pieces just to fit me with the rest
But what if I what if I trip, what if I what if I fall
Then am I the monster yeah, just let me know
what if I what if I sin, what if I what if I break
Then am I the monster yeah, just let me know yeaahhh
I was 15 when the world put me on a pedestal
I had big dreams of doing shows and making memories 
Made some bad moves trying to act cool upset by their jealousy

snippet.title: 【金馬57慶功】李國煌一秒逗樂李安！喊話拍片、主持「免付費」
snippet.description:
第57屆金馬獎順利落幕，《男兒王》獲最佳造型設計肯定，新加坡喜劇天王 #李國煌 雖鎩羽而歸，仍對這次來參加金馬充滿感謝！李安導演典禮後跑滿各大慶功宴，來到《男兒王》場子被國煌哥的幽默逗笑。

國煌哥趁機邀片，還笑說明年願意來主持金馬，兩樣都是「免付費」。李安則阿莎力表示會記得這兩件事，笑說：「那你也要記得這一件事（指免付費）。」

#金馬57｜#慶功直擊｜#李安｜#男兒王

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Leeds vs Arsenal (0-0) | Premier League
snippet.description:
Nicolas Pepe was sent off for the first time in his career but we stood firm to secure a point at Elland Road.

The Ivory Coast winger saw red early in the second half following an off-the-ball clash with Ezgjan Alioski.

We were forced back after that but stout defending, the woodwork and fine goalkeeping from Bernd Leno kept Leeds at bay.

And we almost snatched victory when Bukayo Saka raced through to force a save from Illan Meslier.

An attacking reshuffle saw Willian and Pepe both start, and we were collectively bright and tenacious in the early stages.

Pepe inadvertently hit the crossbar with an attempted cross from the left, and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang slashed a shot high and wide on the turn after excellent work from Hector Bellerin.

Leeds goalkeeper Meslier wasn't tested, but Leno was. He had to save from Patrick Bamford - twice - and chances also came and went for Raphinha, Stuart Dallas and Mateus Klick as Leeds started to get on top.

Mikel Arteta brought on Reiss Nelson at half-time but our gameplan was undermined when Pepe was sent off by Anthony Taylor once the referee had checked footage of his altercation with Alioski.

Leno made a wonderful one-handed save to keep out a Dallas shot that was headed for the top corner, and substitute Rodrigo crashed a shot off the crossbar.

We looked set for a Leeds siege but, instead, we opened up the home side on the break.

One charge ended with an Aubameyang shot that was blocked by Liam Cooper's arm as the defender slid in. On this occasion, VAR was not called upon.

Saka raced through moments later but Meslier stood his ground to block the England international's shot.

Bamford headed against the post and Raphinha hit the bar as Leeds continued to threaten - but we kept a valuable clean sheet.

#arsenal #premierleague #leedsunited

Mikel Arteta brought on Reiss Nelson at half-time but our gameplan was undermined when Pepe was sent off by Anthony Taylor once the referee had checked footage of his altercation with Alioski.

Leno made a wonderful one-handed save to keep out a Dallas shot that was headed for the top corner, and substitute Rodrigo crashed a shot off the crossbar.

We looked set for a Leeds siege but, instead, we opened up the home side on the break.

One charge ended with an Aubameyang shot that was blocked by Liam Cooper's arm as the defender slid in. On this occasion, VAR was not called upon.

Saka raced through moments later but Meslier stood his ground to block the England international's shot.

Bamford headed against the post and Raphinha hit the bar as Leeds continued to threaten - but we kept a valuable clean sheet.

snippet.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fernández, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

snippet.title: Aku Bidadari Syurgamu - Aishah | #SFMM35
snippet.description:
Antara acara yang dinanti-nantikan saban tahun terutamanya buat peminat serta penggiat seni muzik tanah air. Di sinilah pentas penentuan untuk 30 lagu yang telah berjaya mara ke pusingan Muzik Muzik 35 Separuh Akhir dalam perjuangan tahunan ke acara kemuncak Anugerah Juara Lagu.

Lagu manakah yang akan layak ke AJL 35? Nantikan siaran langsung Muzik Muzik 35 Separuh Akhir (SFMM35) di saluran YouTube TV3Malaysia yang akan diadakan selama 3 hari berturut-turut bermula 20 November (Jumaat) sehingga 22 November (Ahad) pada jam 9 malam.

Berikut lagu-lagu yang akan dipertandingkan:

1. Sakit - Zynakal & Yonnyboii
Komposer & Lirik: Yonnyboii & Zynakal

2. Sembah - Naim Daniel ft Man Keedal
Komposer & Lirik: Naim Daniel & Iqie Hugh

3. Panggung - Apex Tajudin
Komposer & Lirik: Faizal Tahir, Mage, Mike Chan, Karim Karam & Romeo

4. Kau Sakiti - Amir Masdi
Komposer & Lirik: Faizal Tahir, Mike Chan, Ezra Kong, Romeo & Mage

5. Tentang Rahsia - Judika & Shila Amzah
Komposer: Farouk Roman
Lirik: Amylea

6. Bicara Rasa - Ariff Bahran & Sarah Suhairi
Komposer & Lirik: Rudy Kasmaran & Sang Hitam

7. Takdir Tercipta - Hafiz Suip & Adira
Komposer: Ikhwan Fatanna & Ayden Ali
Lirik: Ikhwan Fatanna & Arisz Ab Rahman

8. 7 Nasihat - Dato’ Sri Siti Nurhaliza, Kmy Kmo & Luca Sickta
Komposer & Lirik: Kmy Kmo & Luca Sickta

9. Hutang - Floor 88
Komposer: Zai Hamzah
Lirik: Achoi Floor 88

10. Aku Bidadari Syurgamu - Dato’ Sri Siti Nurhaliza
Komposer: Ippo Hafiz
Lirik: Siti Rosmizah

#SFMM35

snippet.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 【地球上最無聊的下午 Nevertheless】Official Music Video
snippet.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升  《#地球上最無聊的下午》MV

沒有人知道 明天有什麼事情在等著
2020這個逼迫人成長的動盪年
每一刻都在教我們要珍惜當下 珍惜身旁的人

於是
We have Plan B

「沒有風 沒有雨 沒有了頑固
沒有甜 沒有苦 也沒了孤獨」
謝謝每一位 支持黃鴻升的地球人
這趟旅程 因為有你們的陪伴 才完整
一雙雙炙熱的眼光 都是 守護外星人的太陽

調皮的他在任務完成後瀟灑退場
留下了「地球上最無聊的下午」這份禮物
TAT＆小怪獸 將剩下的詞完成
而團隊擷取鬼哥過往的聲音素材 克服了技術
希望以Plan B的精神 將這首因愛而生的創作
送給喜歡他的朋友們

想念時 三兩好友或是家人 聚在一起
聊聊天 吃點零食水果 配上你的歌
地球上最無聊的下午
是最平凡也最珍貴的時光

-
「那你的PLAN B是什麼？」
這是他常問別人的ㄧ句話
「最後ㄧ刻的答案 才是我最好的答案」
這是他完成任何事後的註解
「凡事都可以輸！但絕對不能輸在想法！」
這是他人生的座右銘

當事情不如意  可以難過
只要你不放棄就有希望
當人生不順遂  可以停歇
但再向前即是充滿力量

即使全世界放棄 都不能算是結束
唯有自己心中放棄 才是真正結束

寧願逆著風 也不願放棄初衷
PLAN A 失敗了 我依然握有PLAN B

把不可能變可能 更顯珍貴

期待我們在平行時空再次相遇

the story continues on 「Planet B」

謹予此作品致

我的老闆 我的好友 我的老師  我們的家人

                「不完美但真實」
                                                              

                        2020.11.25   Dino & TAT

黃鴻升《地球上最無聊的下午》♫ https://RockRecordsCo.lnk.to/Nevertheless

地球上最無聊的下午 Nevertheless
作曲 Composer：王山而 Ray Hsieh
作詞 Lyricist：黃鴻升 Alien Huang / 小怪獸

沒有風 沒有雨 沒有了頑固
沒有甜 沒有苦 也沒了孤獨
這裡沒有重量 也沒有真相
天使們也不會跳舞

想帶你去澀谷的街上走走
穿越幾萬光年逛逛我的星球
但是外頭 太多 太熱情的面容
日常是誰的茶餘飯後

雖然 我的願望有點老套
可是 有你的微笑就剛好

感謝你 對我 默默的 應援加油
讓辛苦變幸福的小怪獸
（在這危險地球）
把不可能變可能
（讓我不曾墜落）
只想再跟你一起 
玩很大 再鬧一場 
瘋狂的 哭和笑
然後再用力擁抱
（穿越平行時空）
停留在這一刻
（讓我想起怎麼快樂）
刻劃幸福的模樣

很有錢 這世界 買不到幸福
很悠閒 朋友圈 找不到歸屬（避風港）
全宇宙的溫度 剩下科技冷酷
誰錯誰對沒有誰在乎

記得 那一雙雙炙熱的眼光
守護著我 溫暖的太陽

感謝你 對我 默默的 應援加油
讓辛苦變幸福的小怪獸
（在這危險地球）
把不可能變可能
（讓我不曾墜落）
只想再跟你一起 
玩很大 再鬧一場 
瘋狂的 哭和笑
然後再用力擁抱
（穿越平行時空）
停留在這一刻
（讓我想起怎麼快樂）
感受生命的重量

snippet.title: Charli D'Amelio CRIES After Losing 1 MILLION Followers Because of THIS
snippet.description:
Charli D’Amelio broke down on Instagram Live on Thursday after receiving backlash from a video her family posted to YouTube. In the video, the TikTok star, her sister, Dixie D’Amelio, and their parents have dinner with YouTube star James Charles. However, after fans watched the video, they quickly slammed the 16-year-old and her sister, claiming they were disrespectful to the family’s personal chef, Aaron May. Even YouTube star Trisha Paytas weighed in.

Exclusives from #ETonline :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQwITQ__CeH2Y_7g2xeiNDa0vQsROQQgv

60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 — Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this world, consumed by neverending conflict, sometimes only an outsider will get the job done. And that's you.

Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure story from CD PROJEKT RED, is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PC, and Google Stadia on December 10th, 2020. The game will also be playable on Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5 consoles when available.

Pre-order now: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

About the game:
Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure story set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour and body modification. You play as V, a mercenary outlaw going after a one-of-a-kind implant that is the key to immortality. You can customize your character’s cyberware, skillset and playstyle, and explore a vast city where the choices you make shape the story and the world around you.

Learn more:
https://www.cyberpunk.net 
https://www.twitter.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.facebook.com/CyberpunkGame 
https://www.instagram.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.discord.gg/CyberpunkGame
https://www.CyberpunkGame.tumblr.com

Tracks:

Title: Come Close
Created by: Sebastian Robertson and Daniel Davies

Title: Suicide
Created by: Geno Lenardo feat. Valin "ZEALE" Zamerron

Title: Makes Me Feel Better
Created by: Kevin Hastings

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

snippet.title: SHOW DA BLACK FRIDAY AMERICANAS 2020
snippet.description:
Bem-vindos ao Show da Black Friday Americanas, uma transmissão ao vivo com mais de 4 horas de duração! Nosso show é apresentado por Felipe Neto e conta ainda com Fred, do Desimpedidos, Fih e Edu, do Diva Depressão, Fernanda Gentil, Camilla de Lucas, Nobru, Kamille Ramos, além das participações de Fabio Porchat e Camila Coutinho. A live está ao vivo simultaneamente em 6 canais e também no Facebook da Americanas. 



• Comente nas redes sociais com a #showdablackfriday •



E quem ainda não baixou o app Americanas, tem que baixar agora! E também tem que ir conferir as ofertas imperdíveis no site Americanas.com. Ao longo da noite, serão divulgados grandes descontos.



Não deixe de acompanhar a live por um segundo dispositivo! Pode ser no tablet, na tv, no laptop...só assim, vocês não vão perder nenhuma oferta do show! E aproveita e já chama todo mundo da família para assistir junto, hein! Esse show é pra vocês!

Uma última dica: lembre-se de trocar a configuração da live para 1080p, assim você assiste a gente em qualidade HD! E também estamos com um link de acessibilidade aqui embaixo! Clica lá pra conferir:

LINK: https://youtu.be/cv24n649V2c



IMPORTANTE:  Todos envolvidos no Show da Black Friday Americanas - tanto a equipe, quanto os criadores, - seguiram todos os protocolos de segurança na prevenção da COVID-19 para que tudo pudesse acontecer da forma mais segura.

O Show da Black Friday é uma parceria entre Youtube, Play9 e Dia Estúdio. 



===

As estrelas da noite:

Felipe Neto: https://www.youtube.com/felipeneto

Camilla de Lucas: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqLIHbcTtcXmht6xB6WNFcg

Fred (Desimpedidos): https://www.youtube.com//Desimpedidos

Diva Depressão: https://www.youtube.com/divadepressao

Nobru: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqWmLengIKFXRjuL1YyXNSg



Participações:

Fábio Porchat (Porta dos Fundos) - https://www.youtube.com/user/portadosfundos

Camila Coutinho - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg-f8gfT9xt12aZxocaZDrw



Youtube Americanas - https://www.youtube.com/user/CanalAmericanas

Facebook Americanas - https://www.facebook.com/americanascom

snippet.title: SHOW DA BLACK DAS BLACKS MAGALU| AO VIVO | CANAL DA LU I MAGALU
snippet.description:
O maior show da Black Friday, tem no Magalu! Música, humor e, claro, muuuuitas ofertas! Luciano Huck comanda o time de apresentadores e artistas que brilham nessa noite especial. Ao som de Anitta, Gloria Groove, Dilsinho, Zé Neto e Cristiano, Os Barões da Pisadinha e Karol Conka.
Achou que tinha acabado? Tem mais! Fabiana Karla, Jonathan Azevedo, Paulo Vieira, Thaynara OG, Lellê, FutParódias, Pequena Lo, Dudu Rocha, Patricia Ramos e Laura Brito completam a lista de convidados da Lu do Magalu!
Baixe o super app Magalu e fique com um olho no show e o outro nas ofertas https://maga.lu/baixeoapp

snippet.title: ANAVITÓRIA, DUDA BEAT - não passa vontade
snippet.description:
Clique e ouça: https://umusicbrazil.lnk.to/naopassavontade

SIGA AS ANAVITÓRIA:
https://www.facebook.com/anavitoriatocantins
https://www.instagram.com/anavitoria
https://twitter.com/oanavitoria

não passa vontade
(Ana Caetano)
 
Quando é que você chega, amor? 
Tô com saudade de você
Já me arrumei inteira pra te receber 
Eu quero tanto passear contigo

Quando é que você vem, amor? 
O coração chega a doer 
Se tu demora, o dia acaba
E faz chover 
Eu tô querendo te abraçar faz tempo

Eu quero tanto levar você pro mar
Pra gente se banhar 
Deixar meu beijo no teu beijo
E namorar colado até o sol cansar de ficar acordado
E você vai lembrar 

Você vai lembrar de mim
Você vai pedir por mim
Vai se perguntar aaaah aaaaah
Quando é que eu vou chegar 
Você vai lembrar de mim
Você vai pedir por mim 
Vai se perguntar 
Aaaaah

Onde é que eu te encontro, amor?
Tô ensaiando pra te ver 
Já procurei aqui
E nada de você 
Eu quero tanto me enroscar contigo 

Me fala que eu te acho, amor 
E a gente pode se perder 
Invento um canto, uma viagem com você 
Tô te chamando pra mostrar meu mundo 

Eu quero tanto levar você pro mar
Pra gente se banhar 
Deixar minha boca no teu beijo
E namorar colado até o sol cansar de ficar acordado
E você vai lembrar

Olha dentro do meu olho
E não passa vontade não

snippet.title: Zé Vaqueiro - Meia Noite (Vídeo Oficial)
snippet.description:
Vídeo Oficial da música "Meia Noite".
Ouça também nos aplicativos de música: https://Fluve.lnk.to/MeiaNoite
Siga no Instagram - @Ze_VaqueiroOF 
#ZeVaqueiro #Original #MeiaNoite

LETRA:
(Zé malhada) 

Você vai deixar a porta aberta para o nosso encontro
Meia noite estou aí em ponto
Daquele jeito pra gente se amar 

Faz tempo que eu estou te olhando e te desejando
E você sabe fica disfarçando pro seu marido não notar

Eu sei você tava carente pois já me falou
Mais na verdade foi eu quem gostou
Quando a gente fez fez amor

Ce tem meu whatsapp e quando der vontade
E se sentir saudade se sentir carente
Ou  lembrar da gente me chama que eu vou 

No sofá da sala na rede armada
Dentro do banheiro, embaixo do chuveiro
Ou na sua cama a gente faz amor

snippet.title: Confira tudo que aconteceu na noite da décima primeira eliminação I A Fazenda 12

snippet.title: [Performance] CHUNG HA 청하 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)' Performance Video
snippet.description:
CHUNG HA 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)' Performance Video

#CHUNGHA #청하 #R3HAB #DreamofYou #PerformanceVideo

Stream/ Download 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)' : https://ffm.to/chungha_dreamofyou
Subscribe CHUNG HA : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Gxb0gMCh3EPIDLQXeQUog

CHUNG HA, R3HAB Collaboration Single 'Dream of You (with R3HAB)'

K-Pop superstar CHUNG HA releases a collaboration single with world famous DJ & Producer R3HAB. “Dream of You (with R3HAB)” is an electronic/dance track that combines a house beat and a thick bassline. A masterpiece is created from the beautiful harmony of retro sounds generated by strings, brass, and vocoder mixed with the dreamlike sound from the synthesizer. The vocal chopping elements heard within the intro are arranged throughout the song to make the single even more charismatic. You can once again experience the charm of CHUNG HA’s deep mid to low vocals, as heard in her recent single ‘Bad Boy.” This single “Dream of You (with R3HAB)” will excite your ears once again

'청하' 세계적인 DJ & 프로듀서 ‘R3HAB'과 컬래버레이션 싱글을 발매한다.
[Dream of You (with R3HAB)]는 하우스 리듬과 선이 굵은 베이스 라인이 이끄는 일렉트로닉 장르의 곡이다.
스트링, 브라스, 보코더의 레트로한 사운드와 몽환적인 신디사이저 사운드가 어우러져 거칠지만 아름다운 하나의 작품이 완성되었다. 인트로의 매력적인 찹핑 보이스 사운드가 곡의 곳곳에 배치되어 매력적으로 곡을 장식한다. 최근 싱글 'Bad Boy'부터 이어지는 '청하'의 중, 저음의 매력을 다시 한번 느낄 수 있다. 이번 싱글 [Dream of You (with R3HAB)]로 다시 한번 여러분의 귀를 즐겁게 자극할 예정이다.

[CHUNG HA, R3HAB ‘Dream of You (with R3HAB)’ Credits]

snippet.title: Corona-Regeln für Dezember | Pressekonferenz mit Merkel, Müller und Söder
snippet.description:
Im Kampf gegen die Corona-Pandemie haben sich Bund und Länder auf weitere Einschränkungen geeinigt. Der Lockdown-light mit geschlossenen Gastronomie-, Freizeit- und Kultureinrichtungen wird bis 20. Dezember verlängert. Bundeskanzlerin Merkel sagte nach den Beratungen, dass die Maßnahmen voraussichtlich noch bis Anfang Januar gelten werden.

https://www.tagesschau.de/inland/bund-laender-corona-111.html

Es sei notwendig, die Kontakte weiter zu reduzieren, deswegen habe man sich auf weitere Einschränkungen verständigt. Es komme weiterhin auf jeden und jede Einzelne an. Merkel mahnte zu Geduld, Solidarität und Disziplin.

Die Kontaktauflagen werden weiter verschärft: Private Zusammenkünfte müssen auf den eigenen und einen weiteren Haushalt beschränkt werden - maximal fünf Personen sind dann erlaubt. Kinder bis 14 Jahre werden von der Regel ausgenommen.

Für die Weihnachtstage und Silvester sollen diese Regeln gelockert werden. Vom 23. Dezember an sollen Treffen "im engsten Familien- oder Freundeskreis" möglich sein, und zwar bis maximal zehn Personen insgesamt. Dazugehörige Kinder bis 14 Jahre sollen hiervon ausgenommen sein. Die Ausnahmeregelung soll "längstens" bis zum 1. Januar gelten.

Für den Einzelhandel werden die Maßnahmen verschärft. In kleineren Läden soll sich nur ein Kunde pro zehn Quadratmetern aufhalten dürfen, in größeren Geschäften sind es 20 Quadratmeter pro Person.

In den Schulen soll ab der achten Klassenstufe auf Hybrid- und Wechselunterricht gesetzt werden. In besonders stark betroffenen Corona-Hotspots wird es noch restriktivere Maßnahmen als bisher geben.

Nach Angaben der Kanzlerin haben Bund und Länder eine dritte Schwelle bei den Sieben-Tages-Inzidenzen eingezogen. Bei mehr als 200 Neuinfektionen pro 100.000 Einwohnern binnen sieben Tagen müssten noch einmal schärfere Einschränkungen verhängt werden. Dies betreffe zurzeit ganz Berlin sowie 62 Landkreise in Deutschland.

Die Bundesländer können nach den Beschlüssen des Corona-Gipfels künftig abhängig von der Infektionslage entscheiden, ob sie Maßnahmen lockern oder verschärfen. Berlins Regierender Bürgermeister Michael Müller (SPD) sagte im Anschluss an die Gespräche, Bundesländer mit sehr guten Zahlen hätten jetzt die Möglichkeit zur Erleichterung. Gleichzeitig seien Länder mit sehr hohen Infektionszahlen in der Pflicht, sich damit auseinanderzusetzen und mögliche Verschärfungen zu prüfen.

snippet.title: Ruthe.de - Die HNO-WG (Folge 10)
snippet.description:
Idee, Zeichnungen, Stimmen, Skript und Sound: Ralph Ruthe. 
(https://ruthe.de)

Animation und Effekte: Falk (http://couchkartoffelsalat.de)

Stimme "Prinz": Aurel Mertz (https://aurelmertz.de)

Story: Ralph Ruthe, Michael Schilling (http://www.michaelschilling.org/) und Markus Barth (http://markus-barth.de)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Zu Ralph Ruthe:

Ralph Ruthe ist Autor, Musiker, Filmemacher und Cartoonist.
Bereits mit 14 Jahren arbeitete Ruthe als Texter für professionelle Comic-Studios und wurde bald einer der Hauptautoren für Käpt'n Blaubär. Nach seinem Zivildienst veröffentlichte er sein erstes Buch.
1998 begann Ruthe für das MAD-Magazin zu arbeiten, und wurde einer der beliebtesten Zeichner und Autoren.
Seit 2003 konzentriert er sich auf seine Cartoonserie SHIT HAPPENS!, die in vielen Zeitungen und Magazinen in ganz Europa erscheinen. Außerdem arbeitet er regelmäßig an seiner Serie FRÜHREIF, die für eine TV-Umsetzung bearbeitet wurde. 
Von 2005 bis 2008 erhielt er viermal hintereinander für SHIT HAPPENS den Sondermann-Preis der Frankfurter Buchmesse in der Kategorie "Cartoon". 2008 und 2009 gewann der den 1. Preis beim Berliner Kurzfilmfestival "Going Underground".
Mit seiner Multimedia-Comedy-Liveshow tritt er deutschlandweit in ausverkauften Theatern auf.

snippet.title: "Lockdown bis März?" - Lindner attackiert Coronapolitik der Bundesregierung
snippet.description:
Der FDP-Fraktionsvorsitzende Christian Lindner hat der Bundesregierung am Donnerstag im Bundestag kein gutes Zeugnis für ihre Corona-Politik und -Maßnahmen ausstellen wollen. Vor allem kritisierte er die Lockdown-Politik, die zunächst nur für November gelten sollte, nach einem erneuten Länder-Regierungs-Gipfel am Mittwoch aber bis Januar. Und am nächsten Tag spreche der Kanzleramtsminister Helge Braun schon davon, dass der Stillstand bis März zu gehen drohe. Die Herangehensweise, Maßnahmen für alle zu verhängen, sei wenig zielführend und nicht durchhaltbar aus wirtschaftlicher Sicht. Sie drohe laut Lindner, die Innenstädte veröden zu lassen, Amazon noch mehr Marktanteile zuzuspielen, ohne dabei wirklich gegen die Pandemie hilfreich zu sein. Um die Coronamaßnahmen effektiv zu gestalten, müsse man einen Schutzschirm für vulnerable Gruppen errichten, anstatt auf Schulden und Verbote zu setzen.

snippet.localized.title: "Lockdown bis März?" - Lindner attackiert Coronapolitik der Bundesregierung
snippet.localized.description:
Der FDP-Fraktionsvorsitzende Christian Lindner hat der Bundesregierung am Donnerstag im Bundestag kein gutes Zeugnis für ihre Corona-Politik und -Maßnahmen ausstellen wollen. Vor allem kritisierte er die Lockdown-Politik, die zunächst nur für November gelten sollte, nach einem erneuten Länder-Regierungs-Gipfel am Mittwoch aber bis Januar. Und am nächsten Tag spreche der Kanzleramtsminister Helge Braun schon davon, dass der Stillstand bis März zu gehen drohe. Die Herangehensweise, Maßnahmen für alle zu verhängen, sei wenig zielführend und nicht durchhaltbar aus wirtschaftlicher Sicht. Sie drohe laut Lindner, die Innenstädte veröden zu lassen, Amazon noch mehr Marktanteile zuzuspielen, ohne dabei wirklich gegen die Pandemie hilfreich zu sein. Glasschüssel groß: https://kikiskitchen.de/geschirr-co./servieren-und-anrichten/401/ruehrschuessel-transparent-gross?number=10400
Schürzen: https://kikiskitchen.de/search?sSearch=sch%C3%BCrze
Teigrädchen mit Wellen: https://kikiskitchen.de/back-und-kochzubehoer/koch-und-backhelfer/137/kikis-teigraedchen?number=10136
Ausrollstab mit Abstandsscheiben: https://kikiskitchen.de/back-und-kochzubehoer/backzubehoer/480/edelstahl-teigroller-mit-abstandsscheiben?number=10479
Marmor-Nudelholz: https://kikiskitchen.de/search?sSearch=marmor
Backblech, verstellbar & kratzfest:
Winkelpalette Klassik: https://kikiskitchen.de/back-und-kochzubehoer/backzubehoer/138/kikis-winkelpalette-12cm
Breite Hebepalette: https://kikiskitchen.de/back-und-kochzubehoer/koch-und-backhelfer/146/neu-kikis-hebepalette-gewinkelt-10-cm?number=10145
Auskühlgitter: https://kikiskitchen.de/back-und-kochzubehoer/backzubehoer/9/auskuehlgitter-eckig?number=10009
Spritzbeutel NEU Made in Germany: https://kikiskitchen.de/back-und-kochzubehoer/spritzbeutel-tuellen/101/kikis-premium-einweg-spritzbeutel?number=10101
Vanilleextrakt alkoholfrei: https://kikiskitchen.de/kikis-produkte/78/kikis-vanilleextrakt-alkoholfrei/halal-70g?number=10078

🔴 Aktuell könnt ihr 10% sparen mit dem Gutscheincode "blackweek" -
ausgenommen sind Maschinen, Bundles, Gutscheine & Porto

▶️Basisrezept
180 g Zucker 
360 g zimmerwarme (!) Butter 
Prise Salz
1 EL Vanilleextrakt https://kikiskitchen.de/kikis-produkte/78/kikis-vanilleextrakt-alkoholfrei/halal-70g?number=10078
2 Eier (M) 
660 g Mehl 

Butter mit Zucker, Salz und Vanilleextrakt 4 Minuten lang cremig mixen. Eier kurz einrühren. Mehl kurz einrühren. Kühlzeit: 60 Minuten.

1️⃣ Mandel-Plätzchen
Ausreichend für: ca. 70 Stück
Zutaten:
- 30 g gemahlene Mandeln
- 80 g gehobelte Mandeln
- 100 g Vollmilchschokolade oder -kuvertüre 

Gemahlene Mandeln in den Teig einarbeiten. Dünn ausrollen, dann mit dem Teigrädchen in Rechtecke schneiden, gehobelte Mandeln oben drauf legen und backen. Anschließend mit geschmolzener Schokolade oder Kuvertüre verzieren.

6 – 8 Minuten bei 180°C Ober- und Unterhitze

2️⃣Engelsaugen / Husarenkrapfen
Ausreichend für: ca. 60 Stück
Zutaten:
- 4 EL Marmelade
Kleine Kugeln aus Keksteig formen. Mit der Rückseite eines Holzkochlöffels eine Mulde in die Kugeln drücken. Marmelde mit Hilfe einer Spritztülle einfüllen.

180°C Ober- und Unterhitze circa 12 Minuten backen.

 3️⃣ Walnuss -Lebkuchen Plätzchen
Ausreichend für: ca. 70 Stück
Zutaten:
- 1,5 TL Lebkuchengeürz
- 70 Walnüsse
- 300 g Vollmilchkuvertüre

Lebkuchengewürz in den Teig einarbeiten. Bei 180°C Ober- / Unterhitze für 4 Minuten backen und auskühlen lassen. Die Kekse in geschmolzene Kuvertüre eintunken, auf Backpapier ablegen und eine Walnuss auflegen. Anschließend trocknen lassen.

Hat euch das Video gefallen?
Verpasst nichts mehr: 
✔️Abonnieren nicht vergessen.

xoxo Kiki 💖

snippet.title: Böhse Onkelz - Waldstadion Live in Frankfurt 2018 (Teaser)
snippet.description:
Ihr habt es vielfach gewünscht, wir denken dass es genau zur richtigen Zeit kommt, um euch über Corona, Quarantäne und den Winter die Zeit zu vertreiben: Live in Frankfurt 2018.

Vom Fahnenmeer, den der B.O.S.C. organisierte, bis zum euphorischen Schlussakkord eines magischen Abends, den wir nie vergessen werden.
Unser erstes Mal im Waldstadion. IM WALDSTADION!
60.000 Neffen und Nichten, wo sonst die SGE spielt und angefeuert wird.

Zum Erinnern und fürs immer wieder gucken nun das ganze Set. Fast drei Stunden der ganze uns aufwühlende, emotionale Wahnsinn auf 2 DVDs oder 1 Blu-ray. Nicht viel Brimborium, fast schon ein bisschen bootlegmässig, aber in Sound, Gefühl und Bild überwältigend.

Ab 11. Dezember.

Eure Onkelz

#BoehseOnkelz #OnkelzLive #Waldstadion2018

snippet.description:
Die Spurs empfangen Rasgrad am 4. Spieltag der Europa League. In Halbzeit eins sorgt Carlos Vinicius in der 16. und 34. Minute per Doppelschlag  zur 2:0 Führung. Harry Winks trifft in der 63. Na, Story schon fertig geguckt? Dann geht's hier zu Walulis Woche inkl. dem Kettensägen-Fetisch von Elton und den crazy Veschwörer-Channels auf Tik Tok: https://1.ard.de/urlaubsvideos_privat

Gegenderte Sprache - Die Debatte darum ist und bleibt in den Medien ein Riesenthema. Auch die Öffentlich-Rechtlichen stecken mittendrin: Das ZDF gendert und kriegt bei Hart aber fair auf die Fresse. Wer regt sich da so fürchterlich auf? Warum springen Medien so drauf an? Und welche Rollen spielen sie in einem immer aggressiver werdenden Konflikt. Das ist unsere Story.

snippet.title: Plötzlicher Kontaktabbruch: Wie fühlt es sich an, mit seiner Familie Schluss zu machen?
snippet.description:
Triggerwarnung: 
Liebe Community, eine der Protagonistinnen berichtet in einer Szene von einem Vergewaltigungsversuch. Falls Ihr davon selber betroffen seid oder Euch getriggert fühlt, findet Ihr Informationen zu Beratungsstellen weiter unten in der Infobox. Außerdem haben wir Euch die Stelle markiert, damit Ihr sie überspringen könnt. 

00:00 Reportage
02:42 Trigger
03:39 Reportage
------------
Schluss machen mit der eigenen Familie – und das von einem auf den anderen Tag. Häufig schämen sich die Betroffenen für einen plötzlichen Kontaktabbruch zur eigenen Familie oder von Familienmitgliedern. Die wenigsten trauen sich, offen darüber zu sprechen.
Wie oft es zu einem Kontaktabbruch innerhalb der Familie kommt, ist nicht erfasst:
Es gibt keine Studien oder Zahlen darüber, wieviele Menschen in Deutschland sich von ihrer Familie getrennt haben. Viele Betroffene berichten jedoch in verschiedenen Foren und Selbsthilfegruppen über ihre Situation und dem erlittenen Verlust. 
Reporterin Alexa Ramthun will erfahren, wieso Menschen den Kontakt zu ihren Eltern abbrechen, ohne den Grund zu nennen und wie es sich anfühlt, wenn das eigene Kind keinen Kontakt mehr will. 
Protagonistin Anne hat sich vor fünf Jahren von ihrer Familie getrennt und lebt seitdem ein scheinbar glückliches Leben mit ihrem Freund, ihrem Hund und ihren engsten Freunden. Ein klärendes Gespräch mit ihren Eltern gab es nie. Sie haben nie erfahren, aus welchen Gründen  Anne ihre Familie verlassen hat. 
Martina steht dagegen auf der anderen Seite: ihre Tochter hat vor elf Jahren den Kontakt zu ihr abgebrochen, sie kann sich bis heute nicht erklären, wieso. Um den Schmerz, die Hilflosigkeit und die Ungewissheit irgendwie verarbeiten zu können, besucht sie unter anderem regelmäßig eine Selbsthilfegruppe. Reporterin Alexa darf bei einer Sitzung dabei sein und bekommt einen Einblick, wie es in einer solchen Gruppe abläuft. 
Wie gehen verlassene Eltern mit diesem Verlustgefühl um? Lässt der Schmerz irgendwann nach? Und geht es Menschen, die ihre Familie verlassen haben, tatsächlich besser? 
------------
Reporterin: Alexa Ramthun
Kamera: Ilhan Coskun
Schnitt: Manuel Weingärtner, Danny Breuker
------------
